// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-1092 — Mass File Rename (thegentlemen)
// Status: test | Level: high | ID: 100186ba-86b3-53af-89a9-541818372a87

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
